_sText:
This is my thrid map, one of my better ones.

To install: Just place all the files (not readme) in the map folder.

This map can hold about 40 players, really fun when it's full.

The nav file is included so bots and hostages can work.

===========
Version 1.3 Relased

Fixed: The shed doesn't have leaks in it anymore.
Added: Added more detail to one of the spawn rooms.
Changed: The hallway with the couches has less and some different item in it.
